Class CursorIterator<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.grouplens.lenskit.cursors.CursorIterator<T>

    java.util.Iterator<T>

    public class CursorIterator<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<T>

    Simple implementation of an Iterator that wraps a Cursor’s data. This is suitable for use with Iterable.iterator().
